  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Techno BB is a funky Playstation title which players much match up beats as represented by coloured tiles with the ultimate ambition of unleashing a Fever Chain. As it is with all good puzzlers, the gameplay allows players to get involved right away but has hidden and subtle complexities that appear on further inspection which its compulsive gameplay richly deserves.\nIt was developed by Konami and only released in Japan.",
